{"id":21977,"date":"2024-01-19T18:35:58","date_gmt":"2021-05-19T13:05:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=21977"},"modified":"2022-05-31T11:04:26","modified_gmt":"2022-05-31T05:34:26","slug":"dressing-table-ideas-for-small-bedroom","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/dressing-table-ideas-for-small-bedroom\/","title":{"rendered":"Dressing Table Ideas For Small Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Spruce up your home with these beautiful yet compact dressing table ideas for small bedrooms<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the easiest ways to spruce up your bedroom is to include an elegant dressing table. A functional piece of furniture that instantly elevates both yours and the room\u2019s style quotient, having a dressing table originates from an era where presentation mattered. If your home is not sprawling over acres of land, these enviously modern dressing table designs for small bedroom will bring an understated charm to the space. Slow down as you lovingly glam up for a night out or simply enjoy a bit of self-isolated vanity.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Built-In Dressing Table Ideas For Small Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Designed for homes with constrained space, this built-in, practical design brings a sense of luxury to the room. Choose an easily accessible, underutilised corner in your bedroom and create a vanity area there. Lined with beautiful grey laminate, this dressing table design for small bedroom is a space-saving decor hack. You have a bright and inviting place to hold your accessories, perfumes, and make-up while keeping the room clutter-free. Infusing elegance to the room and joy in your life, this cosy nook will be your go-to space when you need to feel relaxed. A full-length mirror with ceiling lights adds to the aesthetics of the room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19143901\/built-in-modern-dressing-table-designs-for-small-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Built in modern dressing table designs for small bedroom with geometrically designed pouffe placed beneath the dressing table\" class=\"wp-image-21978\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19143901\/built-in-modern-dressing-table-designs-for-small-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19143901\/built-in-modern-dressing-table-designs-for-small-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19143901\/built-in-modern-dressing-table-designs-for-small-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19143901\/built-in-modern-dressing-table-designs-for-small-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A matching geometrically designed pouffe placed beneath the dressing table brings a comfortable contemporary vibe to the room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mirrors Work As Dressing Table Ideas For Small Bedroom&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Something is better than nothing, and this simple design renders the fact valid. An understated framed mirror hung along the wardrobe is the easiest way to accommodate a dressing area in a small room. With not enough room to add drawers, use compartments in your cupboard to keep the room mess-free. Having a full-sized mirror will allow you to admire your entire outfit while helping you get a quick glimpse on your way out. Placed on the opposite wall of the window, the full-length mirror also creates the illusion of a more spacious bedroom.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19174921\/mirrors-work-as-dressing-table-ideas-for-small-bedrooms.jpg\" alt=\"Mirrors work as dressing table ideas for small bedrooms with warm yellow ceiling lights right above the mirror\" class=\"wp-image-21994\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19174921\/mirrors-work-as-dressing-table-ideas-for-small-bedrooms.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19174921\/mirrors-work-as-dressing-table-ideas-for-small-bedrooms-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19174921\/mirrors-work-as-dressing-table-ideas-for-small-bedrooms-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19174921\/mirrors-work-as-dressing-table-ideas-for-small-bedrooms-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Place two warm yellow ceiling lights right above the mirror to help you get ready under proper lighting<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gateway To Narnia<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>How beautiful is this dressing table design for small bedroom that opens into a wardrobe? Compact yet complete for all your beauty rituals, this elegant dressing area is created within an empty space of the closet. Matching the all-white bedroom, the dressing space is a brightly lit area where you can comfortably sit down, relax and dress up. A perfect addition to match the luxe tone of the room is a statement back chair that is easily concealable within the wardrobe.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175304\/wardrobe-designs-for-small-bedroom-with-dressing-table-as-gateway-to-narnia.jpg\" alt=\"Wardrobe designs for small bedroom with dressing table as gateway to narnia with open shelves above and a drawer beneath\" class=\"wp-image-21995\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175304\/wardrobe-designs-for-small-bedroom-with-dressing-table-as-gateway-to-narnia.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175304\/wardrobe-designs-for-small-bedroom-with-dressing-table-as-gateway-to-narnia-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175304\/wardrobe-designs-for-small-bedroom-with-dressing-table-as-gateway-to-narnia-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175304\/wardrobe-designs-for-small-bedroom-with-dressing-table-as-gateway-to-narnia-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>With open shelves above and a drawer beneath, you will have ample space to organise your skincare essentials and other nifty items<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bedside Dressing Table Ideas For Small Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>All women want is a dedicated corner that takes up no space yet accommodates all their precious accessories. This elegant vanity is an extension of a bedside cabinet that proudly complements the theme of the room. Neither is it too fanciful nor is it too simple; the cabinet-turned-dressing table is a functional piece of furniture. An understated framed mirror featuring distressed grey paint brings a rustic vibe to an otherwise modern bedroom. The cabinet\u2019s top drawer can be used to store make-up and skincare products, while the bottom two can be used to store daily wear items. A makeshift bedroom chair can be doubled up as your dressing area and as statement furniture in the room.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175442\/bedside-dressing-table-design-for-small-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Bedside dressing table design for small bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-21996\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175442\/bedside-dressing-table-design-for-small-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175442\/bedside-dressing-table-design-for-small-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175442\/bedside-dressing-table-design-for-small-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175442\/bedside-dressing-table-design-for-small-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>If you cannot place ceiling lights above the dressing table, a sophisticated golden table lamp is an easy way to ensure you have proper lighting when dressing up<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dressing Table Ideas For Small Bedroom By The Window<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There\u2019s a certain old-world charm of getting ready by the window, slyly peeping as you wait for your beloved to arrive. A sweet vintage stand-alone foldable table is one of the best modern dressing table designs for small bedroom. The petite table has an equally charming built-in mirror to help you fix all your mascara needs. Small yet sizzling, this girly dressing table may be tiny, but it packs a punch in terms of style and utility.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175833\/dressing-table-for-small-bedroom-by-the-window.jpg\" alt=\"Dressing table for small bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-21999\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175833\/dressing-table-for-small-bedroom-by-the-window.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175833\/dressing-table-for-small-bedroom-by-the-window-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175833\/dressing-table-for-small-bedroom-by-the-window-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/19175833\/dressing-table-for-small-bedroom-by-the-window-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>When not in use, you can fold the mirror inside and use it as a study table. A small pot with fresh flowers brings a refreshing vibe to the space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Consider your dressing table an investment for your bedroom. Compact yet mighty, these modern dressing table designs for small bedroom bring elegance and luxury to a room. A designated space for self-care is no longer considered vanity; it is now routine maintenance of your skin. If you wonder how these stunning dressing table designs will fit into your small bedroom, fret not. Reach out to us at Design Cafe. We will help decorate your room that not only looks great but also maximises space.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you liked reading about dressing table ideas for small bedroom, also have a look at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wall-mounted-dressing-table-designs\/\">wall mounted dressing table designs<\/a><\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \